    This class is used for modeling a console for the Big Two card game.

    Flush class is a subclass of Hand which is used to model a Flush hand with methods to check if the hand is a valid Flush type, and also return the top card of the hand if it is a valid Flush

    FullHouse Class is a subclass of Hand which is used to model a FullHouse hand and check if the hand is a valid FullHouse, and also return the top card of a FullHouse hand
    Hand
    The Hand public class is a subclass of CardList .It models the hand of cards and has private instance variables storing the cards played and methods which check if the played hand is valid, gets the type of hand and also gets the top card
